text: Aigerim Alimkulova (; born 3 September 1990) is a Kazakhstani footballer who plays as a defender. She has been a member of the Kazakhstan women's national team. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Kazakhstani women's footballers Category:Kazakhstan women's international footballers Category:CSHVSM-Kairat players
